Us: we miss dan this is literal hell-

Us: oh hell yeah phil content

Us: look we know that dan needs a break but it’s been months and we’re dying-

Us: look at phil in that instastory he is looking Great

Us: what if dan never comes back what if we never see him again-

Us: phil that tweet omg why is he like this

Us: we have to be prepared for him to never come back maybe this is our new normal-

Us: phil is doing so great look how comfortable in his own skin he’s become

Us: it’s not dan and phil without dan we’re missing a piece of our hearts and each day it gets harder-

Us: phil is our king always bringing us content what a great man he is

Us: we’re so desperate for content we are getting Nothing-

Us: haha look at phil’s new community post yay a new video in a few days
